name: a fantasy color LORA
description:
I originally planned to make a lora model to specialize in creating images for land scapes illus, but for some reason, when combined with anime characters, it adds a lot of interesting effects, so I chose a name harrowing for it
working pretty good with most orther checkpoint file
add ver 2 after I fine tune it
pls give some feed back if you can

modelVersions.name: a_fantasy_color_LORA_V2
modelVersions.description:
Fine tune it with a buch of new imagine, it work pretty good now.

working way greater with anything-v3.vae
